      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">4 Octr 1858 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ Referring to your applicatn ¶  dated 23rd Augt last ¶  I have the honor to request you will state on how many days in the week the horse and cart for watering trees on the St Ki...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">58.10.04</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Balmain</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 58/3124, unit 2, p. 85, VPRS 975/P2 outward registered correspondence, VA 669 Public Works Department, Public Record Office, Victoria</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">4 Octr 1858</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Referring to your applicatn<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">application.</p>
               </note> dated 23rd Augt last<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">sic</seg>. See M to C. Duffy, 23 September 1858.</p>
               </note> I have the honor to request you will state on how many days in the week the horse and cart for watering trees on the St Kilda road is likely to be required; and also for what period this will be necessary; in order that authority for a definite amount being expended may be obtained from the Board of Lands &amp; Works</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Sd for CPW<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Signed for Commissioner of Public Works.</p>
               </note> T. C. Balmain</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The Director of the Botanic Gardens</p>
         </div>
      </body>
